Class DATypeAdapter

java.lang.Object
org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.SclElementAdapter<DataTypeTemplateAdapter,T>

org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.dtt.DATypeAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDataTemplate, IDTTComparable<TDAType>
public class DATypeAdapter extends AbstractDataTypeAdapter<TDAType>
A representation of the model object DAType.

The following features are supported:

  1. Adapter
    • Returns the value of the DataTypeTemplateAdapter reference object
    • Returns the value of the BDAAdapter reference object By BDA name
    • Returns the value of the BDAAdapters containment reference list
    • Returns the value of the DATypeAdapter reference object By BDA name/em>
  2. Principal functions
    • Add TPrivate under this object
    • Returns the value of the TBDA reference object By name
    • Returns List Of ResumedDataTemplate By DaTypeName
    • Returns List Of ResumedDataTemplate By Custom filter
    • Returns Completed list Of ResumedDataTemplate
  3. Checklist functions
    • Compare Two TDA
    • Check structData from DaTypeName
    • Check whether TDA contain TBDA with Struct Btype By Id
    • Check whether TDAType contain contain TEnumType By Id
